Chandler.Desert Breeze Lake:
Desert Breeze Lake is located in Desert Breeze Park in west Chandler, Arizona, USA, southwest of Ray Road and McClintock Drive on Desert Breeze Boulevard.


== Fish species ==
Rainbow trout
Largemouth bass
Sunfish
Catfish (channel)
Tilapia
Carp
